{"tid":331070,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老咪，大圍美林冬菇亭開撚左三間垃圾！！！","createTime":"2017-07-21T20:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T05:01:24.000Z","uid":16697,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b98730ee8336ee2d068a52491c68e7b3a667ab59","tid":331070,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T20:01:36.000Z","msg":"還我茶記，成個美林美松得個翠河連鎖茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冬菇亭裝修後開撚左肉餅弟，屌你老咪乜撚野來架，九唔搭八又貴，開老人邨？60-100 一個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果間日本料理仲on9<br />\n,瘋狂搵打手寫open rice,又賣膳稿，周街廣告，用35$ 魚生飯做綽頭，但每次都賣晒，逼你食貴野<br />\n屌你老咪定價仲貴過尖沙咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中間個糖水鋪算好少少，中式都係20$ 頭，但西式一撚樣50up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一間茶仔都冇開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，睇撚死佢地等執"},{"pid":"45f19c79347dfed5c790524ae2962504fd9b909a","tid":331070,"uid":3254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T20:15:44.000Z","msg":"好立克肉餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲慘過食屎"},{"pid":"547e993c25e75a6eb19c4ab05c4f986db1badfe1","tid":331070,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T00:50:03.000Z","msg":"上咗apple"},{"pid":"f0dffc3b48f816695cebcd701ff6a157a3ef4d14","tid":331070,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上咗apple</blockquote><br />\n垃圾鱔稿"},{"pid":"53144c70dfa4f23d66614e66f0937d6a6fc0b75b","tid":331070,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:06:08.000Z","msg":"糖水果間都OK既<br />\n30幾都埋到單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fcbea8e15879f1928abdd0f5e67ebf393b56eb","tid":331070,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"喺荃灣食過肉餅哥，覺得唔差，係貴咗啲。"},{"pid":"ed2ffb3955a0b69ddfabc9daf0198d377eda17f9","tid":331070,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上咗apple</blockquote><br />\n垃圾鱔稿</blockquote><br />\n細個住咗大圍，全部垃圾食店<br />\n間中返阿媽到垃圾茶記要排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86046764d5a1df5467556e11fc063ca675d62ba","tid":331070,"uid":88094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"間日本野真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又貴又難食 呢個價錢我出去食唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe8f56ba84b42876727bc5d3994775e662797c7","tid":331070,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上咗apple</blockquote><br />\n垃圾鱔稿</blockquote><br />\n細個住咗大圍，全部垃圾食店<br />\n間中返阿媽到垃圾茶記要排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBtw, 美林街市滷水好食"},{"pid":"3f99791127cde173f30a15079a561162f9993cb7","tid":331070,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:20:18.000Z","msg":"經過見到間日本野，見到心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁柒貴等執啦"},{"pid":"c34c1194fc39fc6421f53d3ff5bc67782c6a9869","tid":331070,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間日本野真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又貴又難食 呢個價錢我出去食唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你上open rice 睇全撚部比$寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d28a89afe63180a9a58a8184a8083644a62f252","tid":331070,"uid":53207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"屌重諗住去試添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed112a20870579d0a9c05fcf7079bc7e56ab042c","tid":331070,"uid":89683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"領展遺禍"},{"pid":"fac55ca6d1f8db76d93600663de498768452b576","tid":331070,"uid":6424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:30:11.000Z","msg":"肉餅哥垃圾<br />\n好多唔同味嘅肉餅只係蒸/煎完擺d 味上去<br />\n上次叫碟菜，苦嘅，仲要豉油都冇滴，叫佢比d 豉油，叫我用枱上面個d 甜豉油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問佢要d 蠔油，拎撚左幾個字，出到黎陣味仲要奇撚怪<br />\n狗都唔屌，冇下次"},{"pid":"9cf48f2ee1e7443478d7b7855d726c281c5d9421","tid":331070,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"以前果幾間大中小寶呢"},{"pid":"a30cdfd4e49e3548885bae5ec21f8454b4358fe2","tid":331070,"uid":33840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:38:47.000Z","msg":"日本野幾好喎， 今日先食完個35蚊魚生黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e365745b976fcc1eddd6cac228227a54461478fc","tid":331070,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"大家唔去就執"},{"pid":"9d4f2da525bdaa1aa53502c6f78e1cdacec55a7d","tid":331070,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6dbbd45fc924c35f5032a2b304e1e5eef70f4a","tid":331070,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:08:07.000Z","msg":"甜品鋪出野勁快喎，落完單唔洗3分鐘就有得食"},{"pid":"61794266fe7d243598b5f58a182f2b467aa92432","tid":331070,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:35:09.000Z","msg":"汁撚左佢地啦"},{"pid":"44d24d30797df9d513815ea84b1259c2fe384ebf","tid":331070,"uid":1505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:56:51.000Z","msg":"食左甜品同肉餅，唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058f8459dd3792dd22a725920d6ca8f13897ccd2","tid":331070,"uid":98172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:04:34.000Z","msg":"唉...我都中撚左伏, 見openrice咁多人講間日本野好食, 諗住去試下<br />\n中午點左個140蚊嘅壽司, 得啲下價魚生做料 (三文魚, 有渣嘅吞拿魚, 好韌嘅八爪魚). 啲飯煮得太爛, 好似冇加醋咁, 冇味. <br />\n<br />\n屌, 冇下次"},{"pid":"f74d88bdbd184a83e21c3ba3430268d8ef173a40","tid":331070,"uid":98172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:04:58.000Z","msg":"呢個價錢, 我去德美食好過"},{"pid":"04919e2ed95ff1f3320c1c82aa14852f20af36d7","tid":331070,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:45:37.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n肉餅哥煎肉餅好食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我唔係叫啲咩奇怪口味<br />\n但啲菜飯真係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n隔籬糖水鋪<br />\n西式甜品垃圾<br />\n中式嘅不過不失，但中式糖水呢啲其實好難整得難食<br />\n不過勝在比起大圍火車站啲糖水鋪平啲<br />\n<br />\n日本野就狗也不屌<br />\n三十幾蚊魚生飯基本上係唔會食到<br />\n食過個牛肉飯衰撚過扑嘢家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吉列豬扒炸到柴皮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87368e1a79ed2fed9c16562aeeb03fc625511e2","tid":331070,"uid":75449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個價錢, 我去德美食好過</blockquote><br />\n德美超正呀"}]}